text9 CODE 0 A00 A00 6E 1 2
text10 CODE 0 B5A B5A 3C 1 2
text11 CODE 0 A6E A6E 6A 1 2
text12 CODE 0 86A 86A A4 1 2
text13 CODE 0 7BC 7BC AE 1 2
text14 CODE 0 6FC 6FC C0 1 2
